original: An experimental pale mutant with skinny limbs and dreadful visage. it's strong regenerative prowess is an offset to it's fragile body.
translation: 面色苍白的变种人。它强大的再生能力抵消了它脆弱的身体。

original: "'Madman'? I only crave to change this world for the better, but the remaining humans MUST bind with this POWER, the worthy will live and serve 'US'. The unworthy will die and be gotten rid of like useless chaff!"
translation: “疯子”？我只渴望把这个世界变得更好，但是剩下的人类必须与这种力量结合在一起，有价值的人将生活并为我们服务。不配的人会死，像无用的糠秕一样被除掉！”

original: "'Nevulion'? The prophecy? Hah, the occult mumbo-jumbo. Yet, they were right about EVERYTHING - I AM THE NEVULION, I AM THE PROPHECY and I SHALL BE YOUR DOOM, FEEBLE HUMAN!"
translation: “‘永不放弃’？预言？哈，神秘的胡言乱语。然而，他们对每件事都是正确的——我是永恒的，我是预言，我将成为你的厄运，软弱的人类！”

original: "'Unstoppable'? We are better trained, better equipped, and superior to this scum in every way that counts! ELIMINATE THE TARGET, NOW!"
translation: “‘势不可挡’？我们训练有素，装备精良，在各方面都比这个人渣优越！立刻消灭目标！”

original: "A trespasser! Kill, kill, KILL!"
translation: “入侵者！杀，杀，杀！”

original: "Alli esta!"
translation: “艾莉埃斯塔！”

original: "Can you even imagine what powers 'WE' have managed to acquire? With them, we can put what remains of this world to it's knees and fully subjugate it all!"
translation: “你能想象‘我们’获得了什么样的力量吗？有了他们，我们就可以把这个世界的残存物放在它的膝盖上，完全征服它！”

original: "Cerebros, cerebros, cerebros..."
translation: “大脑，大脑，大脑…”

original: "Coherlo, coherlo, coherlo..."
translation: “科埃洛，科埃洛，科埃洛…”

original: "Each step you make only brings you closer to your death, trespasser!"
translation: “你的每一步都只会让你离死亡更近，入侵者！”

original: "Even if you kill me, you will perish as soon as you come across one of 'THEIR' creations!"
translation: “即使你杀了我，只要你遇到一个‘他们’的创造物，你也会死的！”

original: "Hahaha, that tickles!"
translation: “哈哈哈，真痒！”

original: "Hehehe, that tickles!"
translation: “呵呵，真痒！”

original: "Hey, who turned out the lights?"
translation: 嘿，谁把灯关了

original: "Hostile in the area!"
translation: “在这个地区有敌意！”

original: "How are you still alive? Die already, you feeble puny being!"
translation: “你怎么还活着？快死了，你这个弱小的家伙！”

original: "I have seen beyond the world of skin, the architecture of blood and bone marrow!"
translation: “我已经超越了皮肤的世界，看到了血液和骨髓的结构！”

original: "I have tasted the blood of fallen angels!"
translation: “我尝过堕落天使的血！”

original: "I shall rip and tear what remains of you to my heart's content!"
translation: “我要把你剩下的东西撕碎，让我心满意足！”

original: "Intruder! I need backup, NOW!"
translation: “入侵者！我现在需要支援！”

original: "Intruder!"
translation: “入侵者！”

original: "It all ends HERE!"
translation: “一切到此为止！”

original: "It's all coming together! The prophecy, Nevulion, will feast on your blood!"
translation: “一切都在一起！预言，永不停息，将以你的鲜血为食！”

original: "Matalo!"
translation: “马塔洛！”

original: "My Master will be happy to see your barely recognizable severed head!"
translation: “我的主人会很高兴看到你几乎认不出来的断头！”

original: "Nevulion's blood flows through my veins!"
translation: “奈弗利恩的血流过我的血管！”

original: "No dejes que se escape!"
translation: “没有人可以逃脱！”

original: "No point in hiding, I will find you sooner or later and rip your heart out!"
translation: “没必要躲起来，我迟早会找到你，把你的心撕碎！”

original: "Oi stranger, my eyes does mean I'm one with the walkers."
translation: “噢，陌生人，我的眼睛确实意味着我和步行者是一伙的。”

original: "Prepare for your destruction!"
translation: “准备好毁灭你！”

original: "Secure the perimeter! Eliminate the target, NOW!"
translation: “封锁周边！立刻消灭目标！”

original: "Security breach, REPEAT, security breach!"
translation: “安全漏洞，重复，安全漏洞！”

original: "Such animal strength and relentlessness - you'll be a great sacrifice for Nevulion!"
translation: “这样的动物力量和无情——你将是永不磨灭的伟大牺牲！”

original: "Te voy a romper en pedazos!"
translation: “穿紧身连衣裤！”

original: "The final ritual WILL be completed with a blood sacrifice - and that is YOU!"
translation: “最后的仪式将以献血来完成——那就是你！”

original: "The prophecy IS already happening and your feeble attempts to stop it merely postpone the inevitable, Nevulion has already entered our realm!"
translation: “预言已经发生了，而你无力阻止它的企图只是推迟了不可避免的事情，永远不会发生的事已经进入了我们的领域！”

original: "There you are!"
translation: “你来了！”

original: "We finally meet. EVERYTHING that I'VE WORKED SO DILIGENTLY ON, BUILT, CREATED and you've destroyed, killed, eradicated... you shall pay for EVERYTHING dearly! Then the NEW ERA will begin!"
translation: “我们终于见面了。我辛勤工作的一切，建造的，创造的，你摧毁的，杀死的，根除的。。。你应该为一切付出昂贵的代价！新时代就要开始了！”

original: "Witness the POWER!"
translation: “见证力量！”

original: "You are up against an unbeatable force, prick!"
translation: “你遇到了一股不可战胜的力量，混蛋！”

original: "You could have been someone. Your skills and knowledge - everything gone to waste because of your silly principles!"
translation: “你本来可以成为某个人的。你的技能和知识——因为你愚蠢的原则，一切都白费了！”

original: "You have killed all of my closest and most trusted people. Even though they clearly gave you MULTIPLE chances to RECONSIDER your decision, to acquire the power and join us! Yet, you acted like a vile and inhumane guest - slaughtered them - chomped the hands that wanted to feed YOU!"
translation: “你杀了我所有最亲近最信任的人。尽管他们给了你很多机会重新考虑你的决定，获得权力并加入我们！可是，你却像一个卑鄙的、不人道的客人一样，把他们宰了，还狠狠地咬了那些想喂你的手！”

original: "You really dare to challenge the ever-expanding unbreakable army built to establish 'OUR' New World Order?"
translation: “你真的敢挑战为建立‘我们的’世界新秩序而建立的不断壮大的牢不可破的军队吗？”

original: "You shall NOT defile this holy sanctuary, filthy outsider!"
translation: “你不可玷污这圣所，污秽的外人！”

original: "You strive to destroy this priceless godly organism and anything associated with it as if it's some kind of a plague or a corruption. Oh, but I am FAR from being corrupted - I've awoken from the deepest slumber - the slumber of ignorance!"
translation: “你努力摧毁这个无价的神圣有机体和任何与之相关的东西，就好像它是某种瘟疫或腐败。哦，但我还远没有堕落，我已经从最深的沉睡中醒来了，那是无知的沉睡！”

original: "You will not escape alive!"
translation: “你不会活着逃走的！”

original: "You're a strong warrior, Nevulion would have bestowed a blessing upon you had you not been such a stubborn resistant brat!"
translation: “你是一个坚强的战士，如果你不是一个倔强的反抗者，你决不会得到祝福的！”

original: "You've lost your only chance to redeem yourself - you could just unite with 'US', with ME, to found a new Earth built upon the flesh and bones of the unworthy and filthy ones!"
translation: “你已经失去了救赎自己的唯一机会——你可以和‘我们’，和我联合起来，建立一个新的地球，建立在不值得和肮脏的人的骨肉之上！”

original: "You've made a foolish choice siding with these wimps. With our combined forces - you and 'US' - 'WE' could have asserted our dominance over the ENTIRE world!"
translation: “你做了一个愚蠢的选择站在这些懦夫一边。有了我们的联合力量——你和‘我们’——‘我们’就可以称霸整个世界！”

original: "You've went through hell and you still do not realize what 'WE' are TRULY capable of?"
translation: “你经历了地狱，你还没有意识到‘我们’真正能做什么？”

original: "eyes, lungs, pancreas - so many snacks, so little time!"
translation: “太多的时间了，太多的胰腺，太多了！”

original:
The organization that has been making attempts in gaining control over the Blob and the Nether technologies has gotten into contact with the The Castlelan to our great surprise, The Castlelan gave away some of the samples to them due to all the trouble that it brought to him turning his servants and guards into zombie-like creatures, obviously in exchange for organization's protection, constant supply of resources and one more horrible thing...
 
    The samples were quickly delivered to this their base of operation, in mere weeks they have managed to understand the deadly and powerful potential of that organism that they have managed to acquire, the fundamental knowledge that they've gained is that the ones who were infected with the ordinary samples turned into mindless aggressive felsh-eating beings, but considering the resemblance with The Blob, there IS a possibility of controlling these beings and turning them into minions.
 
    Altering the DNA and forcing mutations of the samples that they've received they finally managed to create a special type of this organism that they've named BL9 that is capable of controlling the beings who were infused with the ordinary types, still retaining their intelligence, now their terrible dream came true - they have created a pretty much fully controllable biological weapon...
translation: 一直试图控制这个小家伙的组织和冥界科技公司接触到了卡斯特兰，这让我们大吃一惊，卡斯特兰把一些样品给了他们，因为这给他带来了很多麻烦，把他的仆人和卫兵变成了僵尸一样的生物，很明显以换取组织的保护，持续的资源供应和更可怕的事情。。。

original: The process of infusion has been completed successfully, now I possess the power that I devoted myself ENTIRELY to, to make it as close to extraterrestrial as possible, now that I can feel it - I realize how much I underestimated it!You will feel it too - you will be forcefully infused with it, either with or without your destruction, NO ESCAPE NOW!
translation: 输液的过程已经成功地完成了，现在我拥有了我全身心投入的力量，让它尽可能地接近外星，现在我能感觉到它——我意识到我是多么地低估了它！你也会感受到它-你将被强有力地注入它，无论你是否被毁灭，现在没有逃脱的可能！

translation: 他们创造了一些特殊的“指挥官”样本，可能会注入他们的将军或关键人物，当然也包括卡斯特兰本人，因为他对这些样本表现出了极大的兴趣，因为他的神秘信仰，还有更多的细节。

original:
This Castle - an enormous magnificent work of art of medievals' engineers, many generations of castlelans were living here pretty much in total isolation from the outer world, they mostly exploited their own rural lands and villages for constant supply of food and water, barely communicating with the modern civilization.
 
    I've heard many rumors about them - that they are dealing with occult beliefs, have created their own religion, do sacrifices even, believing in the `returning` of some kind of a chaotic deity that would destroy our entire world's human population, it's civilization entirely to restore the balance, build a new world, a new civilization with the aid of that deity.
 
    Not a long while after the Cataclysm, thanks to our portable radars and scout drones we have noticed some very strong signal interferences that not only jammed everything but burned to the crisp both our radars and drones, the magnitude and the radius of the EMP damage was incredibly big, unlike any interference we've ever seen.
 
    Eventually we've found out that the cause of this was a shimmering portal appearing for a certain amount of time in the mines under that Castle, which spawned a new type of blob it seems that by this time has already fully infused with the inhabitants of The Castle, one of our spies pretending to be a goods trader managed to lure out some of the guards outside, as soon as she approached them, they attacked her in a very aggressive manner trying to eat her flesh murmuring some strange gibberish...
translation:
这座城堡是中世纪工程师的宏伟艺术杰作，许多代卡斯特伦人都生活在这里，几乎完全与外界隔绝，他们主要利用自己的农村土地和村庄来持续供应食物和水，几乎没有与现代文明交流。
我听过很多关于他们的谣言-他们正在处理神秘的信仰，创造自己的宗教，甚至做牺牲，相信某种混乱的神的“回归”会摧毁我们整个世界的人口，这是文明完全恢复平衡，建立一个新的世界，在那个神的帮助下一个新的文明。

灾难发生后不久，多亏了我们的便携式雷达和侦察机，我们注意到一些非常强的信号干扰，不仅干扰了一切，而且烧毁了我们的雷达和无人机，电磁脉冲伤害的大小和半径都非常大，与我们所见过的任何干扰不同。

最终我们发现，造成这种情况的原因是一个闪闪发光的入口在城堡下的矿井中出现了一段时间，它产生了一种新型的斑点，似乎此时已经完全充满了城堡的居民，我们的一个间谍假装是一个货物贩子设法把外面的一些警卫引诱出来，她一走近他们，他们就用非常咄咄逼人的方式攻击她，试图吃掉她的肉，嘴里咕哝着一些奇怪的胡言乱语…

translation: 你在燃烧！因为你站在熔岩里！

original: You are in the sewers - great, but BEWARE, Castlelan is not joking about his Right Hand, it's not a mere crazed cultist, it is a tall lizard-skinned incredibly agile and deadly creature that is capable of hiding in the shadows, one of `THEIR` bioweapons it seems, it guards the path to the mines below, use your wits and skills to DESTROY it!
translation: 你在下水道里-很好，但是要小心，卡斯特兰不是在开他的右手玩笑，它不是一个疯狂的邪教分子，它是一个高大的蜥蜴皮肤，非常敏捷和致命的生物，能够隐藏在阴影中，似乎是他们的一种生物武器，它守卫着通往下面地雷的道路，用你的智慧和技能摧毁它！

original: You are truly surprising me now, you have eliminated even my most loyal general - not much of a loss anyway, I'll have a dozens more if needed, the final Island's fortress is standing tall - it will slow you down allowing me to fully infuse with BL9
translation: 你现在真让我吃惊，你甚至连我最忠诚的将军都被淘汰了——反正损失不大，如果需要的话，我还会有几十个，最后一座岛的要塞矗立着——它会让你放慢速度，让我完全注入BL9

original: You carefully examine the map and spot multiple strange looking entrances that lead to some kinds of underground biomes...more BL9 infestation...
translation: 你仔细检查地图，发现了多个奇怪的入口，导致了一些地下生物群落…更多的BL9感染。。。

original: You carefully examine the map and spot the entrance of The Castle, it says 'The bridge leads to the main gates'
translation: 你仔细检查地图，找到城堡的入口，上面写着“桥通向正门”

original: You carefully examine the map and spot the way to reach the Island, apparently in order to get through you'll have to navigate through multiple cave structures and surface military camp...
translation: 你仔细检查地图，找出到达岛上的路，很明显，为了通过，你必须穿过多个洞穴结构和地面军营。。。

original: You consume the herb and you feel very well healed!
translation: 你吃了这个药草，你感觉很好的治愈了！

original: You consume the herb and you feel well-healed to a certain extent!
translation: 你吃了这个药草，一定程度上你感觉好了！

original: You consume the herb and your wounds are slightly healed up!
translation: 你吃了药草，伤口就稍微愈合了！

original: You have been given a choice - you chose poorly, foolishly - and now there will be severe consequences for this, you will not escape alive from the military base - what awaits you BENEATH it is BEYOND your imagination!
translation: 你被赋予了一个选择——你的选择很糟糕，愚蠢——而现在这将带来严重的后果，你将无法从军事基地活着逃脱——在它下面等待你的是你想象不到的！

original: You have managed to enter `OUR` base of operations - the militarized Island guarded by very well-trained biologically enhanced soldiers armed to teeth, plenty of which are heavily mutated having inhumane strength and agility, that Castle - that was a mere cult controlled by an archaic madman - I would have got rid of them myself upon starting our conquest, but you've done me a good favor, the first time - the last time, survivor...
translation: 你成功地进入了“我们的”作战基地——这座军事化的岛屿，由训练有素的生物强化士兵守卫着，他们武装到牙齿，其中许多人都有着非人的力量和敏捷，大量变异，这座城堡——那只是一个由古老的疯子控制的邪教——我在开始我们的战斗时会自己除掉他们征服，但你帮了我一个大忙，第一次-最后一次，幸存者。。。

original: You have reached the destination, I am glad to see you alive!Infiltrating the Island you will come across camps, some small military structures - but that's just the tip of the iceberg - the only way to get inside of The Island's bunker and more elaborate structures is via water caves
translation: 你已经到达目的地了，我很高兴看到你活着！渗透到岛上，你会看到营地，一些小型军事建筑——但这只是冰山一角——进入岛上碉堡和更复杂建筑的唯一途径是通过水洞

original: You have taken some healing herbs.  It appears to have panacea-like effects along with radioation cleansing properties slowly cleansing your body of radiation; if you take more of it, you'll be able to speed up the process.
translation: 你吃了一些草药。它似乎有灵丹妙药般的效果，同时具有辐射净化的特性，可以慢慢清除体内的辐射；如果你服用更多，你就能加快这个过程。

original: You have witnessed our work of art - incredibly fast regenerating humanoids - with enough time, we can make truly immortal humans, extend humans' limits, you cannot even conceive of what power you may achieve!Think of this - how about you stop while you still can, turn your back on this wanna-be-heroic bunch of fools and become a part of my personal army - so we can establish The New Order together, huh?
translation: 你已经见证了我们的艺术作品——难以置信的快速再生的类人机器人——只要有足够的时间，我们就能创造出真正不朽的人类，扩展人类的极限，你甚至无法想象你能获得什么样的力量！想一想-趁你还可以的时候停下来，把这帮想成为英雄的傻瓜抛在脑后，成为我个人军队的一部分-这样我们就可以一起建立新秩序了，嗯？

original: You made it through!Good, now in order to reach the surface of The Island once again you will have to pass through a long basement passage, be aware though - it is heavily guarded as far as I know...
translation: 你成功了！很好，现在为了再次到达岛的表面，你必须穿过一条长长的地下通道，但要注意——据我所知，这里戒备森严。。。

original: You teleport to the attuned gate!
translation: 你传送到调谐门！

original: You're getting there, in order to reach The Castlelan and put the final exclamation mark to everything that had led to this point you will have to cross the bridge leading to the final tower of The Castle, stop the madman at all costs!
translation: 你到了那里，为了到达城堡，并把最后的感叹号，一切导致这一点，你将不得不通过桥梁，导致城堡的最后塔，阻止疯子不惜一切代价！

original:
You're probably wondering who I am - I am an agent working on one of the remnants of many secret organizations that existed pre-Cataclysm.I was born in one of it's main hidden facilities, my father was a retired military officer who was hired as a mercenary and worked long for this organization, they had predicted the Cataclysm long before it occurred.
 
    Obviously, such organizations had and many still have many hidden facilities, vaults, many different structures, an unbelievable amount of resources to feed and supply multiple generations' of survivors and it's agents' offspring.
 
    For many years I've been  training diligently to become not just a survivor and a scavenger - but an agent who can search and scavenge for rare resources as well along with the basic ones if not for flourishment but at the very least continued existence and survival of our organization and my people...
translation: 你可能想知道我是谁-我是一名特工，在大灾变前存在的许多秘密组织的残余中工作。我出生在那里的一个主要的秘密设施里，我父亲是一名退休军官，他被雇佣为雇佣兵，为这个组织工作了很长时间，他们早在灾难发生之前就预测到了。

original: You've gotten far, I have to admit this, but it all ends here, you won't escape alive from my mind-boggling garden full of surprises, besides, the annoying squashable bugs is not the only thing you are going to see here in my Castle...
translation: 你已经走得很远了，我不得不承认这一点，但一切都在这里结束了，你不会从我那令人难以置信的充满惊喜的花园里活着逃走，况且，在我的城堡里，你会看到的不仅仅是那些烦人的臭虫。。。

original: Your foolishness and stubbornness has no end, there's no stopping it!Now even I am involved into this!You do know that you're prolonging the Cataclysm with your actions?The BL9 is the only way to stop this and end BOTH the Blob and Mycus, restore the civilization but ONLY with the worthy society - everyone else that falls short of our expectations shall be eradicated!
translation: 你的愚蠢和固执是没有尽头的，没有办法阻止它！现在连我都被牵扯进来了！你知道你在用你的行动延长灾难吗？BL9是阻止这一切的唯一途径，结束了这一切，恢复了文明，但只有建立了一个有价值的社会——所有不符合我们期望的人都将被铲除！
